seful and how to improve the site. No personally identifiable information is collected through analytics.</p><h2 style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:700;margin-top:32px;margin-bottom:12px\">Cookies</h2><p style=\"font-size:15px;color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:16px\">We use minimal cookies necessary for analytics functionality. We do not use advertising cookies or share cookie data with third parties.</p><h2 style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:700;margin-top:32px;margin-bottom:12px\">Local Storage</h2><p style=\"font-size:15px;color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:16px\">Some tools may use your browser&#x27;s local storage to save preferences or settings between visits. This data is stored only on your device and is never transmitted to us.</p><h2 style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:700;margin-top:32px;margin-bottom:12px\">Third-Party Services</h2><p style=\"font-size:15px;color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:16px\">The only third-party service we use is Google Analytics for anonymous usage statistics. We do not use any advertising networks, social media tracking pixels, or other third-party data collection tools.</p><h2 style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:700;margin-top:32px;margin-bottom:12px\">Changes</h2><p style=\"font-size:15px;color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:16px\">We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page with an updated date.</p><h2 style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:700;margin-top:32px;margin-bottom:12px\">Contact</h2><p style=\"font-size:15px;color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:16px\">If you have questions about this privacy policy, please reach out through our website.</p></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer style=\"border-top:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--bg-secondary);padding:48px 24px 32px;margin-top:auto\"><div style=\"max-width:var(--max-width);margin:0 auto;display:flex;flex-